        "text": "Continuous Emission Rate Monitoring: The Permittee shall install, certify, operate, and maintain a\ncontinuous flow monitoring system (EQUI 145) meeting the requirements of Performance\nSpecification 6 of Appendix B of 40 CFR pt. 60 and the calibration drift (CD) assessment, relative\naccuracy test audit (RATA), and reporting provisions of Procedure 1 of Appendix F of 40 CFR pt. 60,\nand shall record the output of the system for measuring the volumetric flow rate of exhaust gases\ndischarged to the atmosphere from EQUI 19 (Boiler No. 2).",
