        "text": "Sulfur Dioxide: Emissions Monitoring: The Permittee shall use the SO2 CEMS (EQUI 51) to measure\nSO2 emissions from EQUI 19 (Boiler No. 2) in pounds per hour (lb/hr). See Subject Item EQUI 51 (SO2\nCEMS) for specific CEMS operating requirements.",
