        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.3.9",
        "page": 37,
        "text": "Nitrogen Oxides: Emissions Monitoring: The Permittee shall use the NOx CEMS (EQUI 38) to measure\nNOx emissions from EQUI 19 (Boiler No. 2) in pounds per hour (lb/hr). See Subject Item EQUI 38 (NOx\nCEMS) for specific CEMS operating requirements.",
