        "subjectItemTitle": "CEMS",
        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.3.18",
        "page": 38,
        "text": "Recordkeeping: The Permittee shall retain records of all CEMS monitoring data and support\ninformation for a period of five years from the date of the monitoring sample, measurement or\nreport. Records shall be kept at the source.",
        "citation": "[40 CFR 60.7(f), Minn. R. 7017.1130, Minn. R. 7019.0100, subp. 1]",
