        "requirementNumber": "5.4.2",
        "page": 38,
        "text": "Opacity: Emissions Monitoring: The Permittee shall use a COMS (EQUI 43) to measure opacity\nemissions from EQUI 19 (Boiler No. 2).",
        "citation": "[40 CFR 60.13, 40 CFR 60.45(a), Minn. R. 7011.0555,\nMinn. R. 7017.1006, Minn. R. 7017.1010, subp. 1(A)]",
