        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.4.3",
        "page": 38,
        "text": "Opacity: Emissions Monitoring: The Permittee shall use a COMS (EQUI 42) to measure opacity\nemissions from EQUI 18 (Boiler No. 2).",
