        "subjectItemTitle": "COMS",
        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.4.4",
        "page": 38,
        "text": "Continuous Operation: COMS must be operated and data recorded during all periods of emission unit\noperation including periods of emission unit start-up, shutdown, or malfunction except for periods of\nacceptable monitor downtime. This requirement applies whether or not a numerical emission limit\napplies during these periods. A COMS must not be bypassed except in emergencies where failure to\nbypass would endanger human health, safety, or plant equipment.",
