        "subjectItemTitle": "COMS",
        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.4.5",
        "page": 38,
        "text": "Monitoring Data: All COMS data must be reduced to six-minute averages. Six-minute opacity averages\nshall be calculated from 36 or more data points equally spaced over each six-minute period.",
