        "text": "QC Program: the facility owner or operator must conduct quality assurance and quality control as\nspecified in Procedure 3 - Quality Assurance Requirements for Continuous Opacity Monitoring\nSystems at Stationary Sources, 40 CFR Pt. 60, Appendix F.",
