        "text": "COMS Calibration Error Audit: due before end of each calendar half-year following permit issuance.\nConduct three point calibration error audits at least 3 months apart but no greater than 8 months\napart.  Conduct audits in accordance with Minn. R. 7017.1220, subp. 3.",
