        "requirementNumber": "5.4.12",
        "page": 39,
        "text": "Notification of Compliance Status: Due 30 days before performance test required by 40 CFR 60.8 if\nCOMS data results will be used in lieu of 40 CFR, Part 60, Appendix A, Method 9 observation data to\ndetermine compliance with the opacity standard as allowed by 40 CFR 60.11(e)(5).",
