        "page": 45,
        "text": "The Permittee shall limit Mercury <= 0.0000054 pounds per million Btu heat input or 0.0000062\npounds per million Btu of steam output. This emission limit applies at all times EQUI 18 is operating,\nexcept during periods of startup and shutdown during which time the Permittee must comply only\nwith items 5 and 6 of Table 3 to 40 CFR pt. 63, subp. DDDDD.",
