        "requirementNumber": "5.10.17",
        "page": 45,
        "text": "The Permittee shall limit Carbon Monoxide <= 150 parts per million 30-day rolling average on a dry\nbasis corrected to 3 percent oxygen. This emission limit applies at all times EQUI 18 is operating,\nexcept during periods of startup and shutdown during which time the Permittee must comply only\nwith items 5 and 6 of Table 3 to 40 CFR pt. 63, subp. DDDDD.",
