        "subjectItemTitle": "Boiler No. 1",
        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.10.32",
        "page": 48,
        "text": "Steam Flow: Parametric Monitoring: The Permittee shall use a steam flow meter (EQUI 152) to\nmeasure the steam flow from EQUI 18.",
        "citation": "[40 CFR pt. 63, subp. DDDDD(Table 8)(item 10),\nMinn. R. 7011.7050, Minn. R. 7017.2025, subp. 3]",
