        "requirementNumber": "5.10.33",
        "page": 48,
        "text": "Parametric Oxygen: Parametric Monitoring: The Permittee shall use an oxygen analyzer (EQUI 146) to\nmeasure the oxygen concentration of the EQUI 18 flue gas.",
        "citation": "[40 CFR pt. 63, subp. DDDDD(Table 8)(item 9), Minn. R. 7011.7050]",
        "referencedIds": [],
