        "text": "The Permittee shall limit Filterable Particulate Matter <= 0.039 pounds per million Btu heat input or\n0.041 pounds per million Btu steam output (front-half particulate matter), or the Total Selected\nMetals (TSM) limit below. This emission limit applies at all times EQUI 19 is operating, except during\nperiods of startup and shutdown during which time the Permittee must comply only with items 5 and\n6 of Table 3 to 40 CFR pt. 63, subp. DDDDD.",
