        "requirementNumber": "5.11.14",
        "page": 55,
        "text": "When different fossil fuels are burned simultaneously in any combination, the applicable nitrogen\ndioxide standard (in lb/MMBtu) shall be determined by proration using the formula provided in\n40 CFR 60.44(b).",
        "citation": "[40 CFR 60.44(b), Minn. R. 7011.0555]",
