        "subjectItemTitle": "Boiler No. 2",
        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.11.42",
        "page": 64,
        "text": "Performance Testing Recordkeeping: During each performance test, the Permittee must record and\nmaintain, at a minimum, the process and control parameters as detailed in Appendix D to this permit.\nThese records must be included with the performance test results and submitted to the\nCommissioner with the performance test report.",
        "citation": "[Minn. R. 7007.0800, subps. 4-5, Minn. R. 7017.2020, subp. 1, Minn. R. 7017.2020, subp. 3,\nTitle I Condition: 40 CFR 52.21(k)(modeling) and Minn. R. 7007.3000]",
        "referencedIds": [],
