        "text": "See subject items STRU 19 (North Pellet Cooler Baghouse Exhaust) and STRU 20 (South Pellet Cooler\nBaghouse Exhaust) of this permit for associated air dispersion modeling-based emission limits and\nperformance testing requirements.",
