        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.20.6",
        "page": 71,
        "text": "Process Throughput: Daily Recordkeeping. On each day of operation, the Permittee shall calculate,\nrecord, and maintain a record of each 8-hour block average pellet loadout rate. This shall be based on\nthe pellet throughput rate collected and recorded by the Process Information Management System\n(PIMS).",
