        "requirementNumber": "5.219.8",
        "page": 120,
        "text": "Pressure Drop: Recordkeeping. The Permittee shall record the time and date of each pressure drop\nreading and whether or not the recorded pressure drop was within the range specified in this permit.",
        "citation": "[Minn. R. 7007.0800, subps. 4-5]",
