        "text": "Monitoring Equipment: The Permittee shall install and maintain the necessary monitoring equipment\nfor measuring and recording pressure drop as required by this permit. The monitoring equipment\nmust be installed, in use, and properly maintained when the monitored fabric filter is in operation.",
        "citation": "[Minn. R. 7007.0800, subp. 4]",
