        "subjectItemTitle": "Fabric Filter - Low Temperature, i.e., T<180 Degrees F",
        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.227.16",
        "page": 133,
        "text": "As required by 40 CFR 64.9(a)(2), for the Semi-Annual Deviations Report required by this permit\nand/or the Notification of Deviations Endangering Human Health and the Environment required by\nthis permit, as applicable, the Permittee shall include the following related to the monitoring\nidentified as required by 40 CFR pt. 64: 1) Summary information on the number, duration, and cause\nof excursions or exceedances, as applicable, and the corrective action taken; and 2) Summary\ninformation on the number, duration, and cause for monitor downtime incidents.",
        "citation": "[40 CFR 64.9(a)(2), Minn. R. 7017.0200]",
