        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.232.8",
        "page": 141,
        "text": "The Permittee shall maintain and operate a pressure drop monitoring device that continuously\nindicates and records the pressure drop across the baghouse.",
        "citation": "[40 CFR 64.3(b)(4)(ii), Minn. R. 7007.0800, subp. 14, Minn. R. 7007.0800, subp. 2(A),\nMinn. R. 7017.0200, Title I Condition: 40 CFR 52.21(k)(modeling) and Minn. R. 7007.3000]",
