        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.232.9",
        "page": 142,
        "text": "The Permittee shall maintain a continuous hard copy readout or computer disk file of the pressure\ndrop readings. Readings outside the range specified in this permit are considered Deviations as\ndefined by Minn. R. 7007.0100, subp. 8a.",
        "citation": "[40 CFR 64.9(b), Minn. R. 7007.0800, subp. 14, Minn. R. 7007.0800, subp. 2(A),\nMinn. R. 7017.0200, Title I Condition: 40 CFR 52.21(k)(modeling) and Minn. R. 7007.3000]",
        "referencedIds": [],
