        "requirementNumber": "5.238.7",
        "page": 158,
        "text": "The Permittee shall operate and maintain the fabric filter in accordance with the Operation and\nMaintenance (O & M) Plan. The Permittee shall keep copies of the O & M Plan available onsite for use\nby staff and MPCA staff.",
        "citation": "[Minn. R. 7007.0800, subp. 14]",
