        "requirementNumber": "5.238.8",
        "page": 158,
        "text": "Daily Inspections: The Permittee shall do the following, once every 24 hours:\nRead and record the pressure drop across the fabric filter.",
        "citation": "[40 CFR 64.3, Minn. R. 7017.0200, Title I Condition: Avoid major modification under\n40 CFR 52.21(b)(2) and Minn. R. 7007.3000]",
        "referencedIds": [],
