        "section": "5",
        "requirementNumber": "5.238.10",
        "page": 158,
        "text": "Pressure Drop: Monitoring Equipment: The Permittee shall install and maintain the necessary\nmonitoring equipment for measuring and recording pressure drop as required by this permit. The\nmonitoring equipment must be installed, in use, and properly maintained when the monitored fabric\nfilter is in operation.",
        "citation": "[40 CFR 64.7(b), Minn. R. 7017.0200]",
        "referencedIds": [],
