        "text": "The Permittee shall operate and maintain control equipment such that it achieves a control efficiency\nfor PM < 10 micron >= 93 percent control efficiency.",
        "citation": "[Title I Condition: Avoid major modification under 40 CFR 52.21(b)(2) and Minn. R. 7007.3000]",
        "referencedIds": [],
