        "text": "The Permittee shall operate and maintain control equipment such that it achieves a control efficiency\nfor PM < 2.5 micron >= 93 percent control efficiency.",
        "citation": "[Minn. R. 7007.0800, subp. 14, Minn. R. 7007.0800, subp. 2(A)]",
